gov.usgs.alarm

Class SNWGroupEventProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • gov.usgs.alarm.SNWGroupEventProcess
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public final class SNWGroupEventProcess
extends java.lang.Thread
    This class built the original events for the SNW groups. It sends events if the mins for bad and warnings are not met. The StatusServer property must be set via properties in edge.prop
